channel.title: Need a client with LOTS of customs (non-renamed)!
channel.description: I need a client with LOTS of customs, it needs to be non-renamed so no itemdef, only class8. It needs to be easy to rip the customs from it, I.e there is nothing I need to decompile. I rather a client with actual customs and not just recolors, I do really need like one with 300+ in it like mikescape or project rainbow but I can't really rip the customs from them. Thanks in advance.
